SUMMARY:**10 AM** Portland Heights Stair Walk
DESCRIPTION:Portland City Trail Walking Group\nHidden stairways\, paths between fabulous homes\, and a pedestrian bridge\, all thru one of the most expensive neighborhoods in Portland. 4+ miles\, lots of climbing!\nFrom the book\, Portland Stair Walks\,” by Laura O.Foster.\nMeet by the vacant grocery store (former Strohecher's) at 2855 SW Patton St.\n**Parking: Across the street on Old Orchard Road or at the lot several hundred feet up Patton from the start.**
